{"id": 1807, "genre": 1000, "title": "网络生活中的这些凑合，你也有吗？", "description": "或者说，上网的时候，你有哪些“忍一忍也行”的时刻？", "record_count": 27973, "comment_count": 51, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170719104006ZBhXpCINGe94arvk.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-20T17:00:18Z", "questions": [{"id": 2628, "title": "网络生活中的这些凑合，你也有吗？", "content": "网络生活中的这些凑合，你也有吗？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 222790, "content": "不喜欢播放器广告，但也不想充会员，就一直忍着", "image": "img/option/option/20170719145901fXQi1bhmZTEwygN2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222792, "content": "为了在一家电商买齐所有东西，换几个常用品牌也行", "image": "img/option/option/20170719150424CTRi5covze0O4jyr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222806, "content": "看上的国外品牌，没有直邮或者靠谱电商或者代购，就不买了", "image": "img/option/option/20170719170005dJZProKvsj2ALBim.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222809, "content": "用习惯了的网站、App更新一些莫名其妙的功能，也会忍着，接着用", "image": "img/option/option/20170719165425eS35Oq1p2lJPkVzd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222810, "content": "网速不够，看剧宁愿看不那么清晰的版本，也懒得下载", "image": "img/option/option/20170719170233z5n3uRyqisWNx6BV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222812, "content": "虽然要仔细鉴别广告，还是会图方便用百度搜索", "image": "img/option/option/2017071917105716WIqNOATsrZ2Yyz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 222847, "content": "知道上网时很多行为都可能泄露隐私，却懒得仔细做隐私设置", "image": "img/option/option/201707191149266x23CWYiodpOgRFB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 223051, "content": "下了很多效率软件，但是懒得学，需要做计划还是纸上随便写写", "image": "img/option/option/20170719145227ZVLvn0fUJrW9Qq1N.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 223052, "content": "除了那些非用不可的App，看到一定要注册才能看/发内容的，会直接离开", "image": "img/option/option/20170719164621C2pefJy5KTkASuwL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}